_sText:
This map is created for your enjoyment, it is very balanced and perfectly symmetrical. It has custom decals and sounds and an overview but everything is pakrat'd so that it is easier to download and easier for the user. No folders, no mess. Enjoy! 

Edit - I recently found out that I had placed the overview wrong into the BSP sorry but you will have to re-download it to see it properly.

Double edit - The overview somehow became corrupted and now I need to remake it I will be taking the map down for a couple of minutes to rectify this, sorry! You can download a version without the purple and black overview till then.

Final edit - I got the overview working and pak'd it for you, download and enjoy!
